		\hline
		$P(l)$&0 &1.5 &3 &4.5& 6&7.5 &9 &10.5 &12 &13.5 &15  \\
		\hline
		$A(l)$ & 0 & $\frac{1}{8} = 0.125$& 0.5 &$\frac{9}{8} = 1.125$ & 2 & $\frac{25}{8} = 3,125$ & $\frac{9}{2} = 4.5$ & $\frac{49}{8} = 6.125$& 8 & $\frac{81}{8} = 10.125$ & $\frac{25}{2} = 12.5$\\
		
